<paragraph id="B2350B0AFFFB2E2B26C7FD92FEDFFEF2" blockId="8.[151,1436,151,501]" pageId="8" pageNumber="273">
<taxonomicName id="758A7089FFFB2E2B26C7FD92FE97FF5F" box="[199,319,151,176]" class="Crustacea (awaiting allocation)" family="Crustacea (awaiting allocation)" genus="Mesosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Crustacea (awaiting allocation)" pageId="8" pageNumber="273" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80FED718FFFB2E2B26C7FD92FE97FF5F" box="[199,319,151,176]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="273">Mesosoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Tergite I 1.7× as long as posteriorly wide, lateromedian carina weak, extending about 0.3× length of tergite, smooth, with isolated punctures laterally on the apical half; tergite II 1.6× as long as posteriorly wide; laterotergite II very narrow, about 0.1× as wide as long; laterotergite III about 0.3× as wide as long, wedge-shaped, mesal edge straight.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B2350B0AFFFB2E2B26C7FC22FB15FE8A" blockId="8.[151,1436,151,501]" pageId="8" pageNumber="273">
<emphasis id="80FED718FFFB2E2B26C7FC22FEBEFEAE" box="[199,278,295,321]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="273">Colour</emphasis>
. Body entirely black with intense blue to purple reflections (
<figureCitation id="2AB1178FFFFB2E2B25B1FC22FB93FEAE" box="[945,1083,295,321]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1951,1975]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1209,1926]" captionTargetId="figure-457@7.[151,1436,1209,1927]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 4. Details of Forrestopius nasutus, sp. nov. A. Habitus of female, in lateral view (scale bar = 2 mm) B. Head and pronotum, in lateral view C. Facial view D. Head and mesosoma, in dorsal view. E. Mandibles." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5531255" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5531255/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="273">Figs 4A, 4D</figureCitation>
) except on clypeus, lower head, mandibles, palpi, antennae, tibiae, tarsi, laterotergites and sterna. Ovipositor valvae testaceous.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B2350B0AFFFB2E2B26C7FC6AFE28FE66" blockId="8.[151,1436,151,501]" box="[199,384,367,393]" pageId="8" pageNumber="273">
<emphasis id="80FED718FFFB2E2B26C7FC6AFEACFE66" bold="true" box="[199,260,367,393]" pageId="8" pageNumber="273">Male</emphasis>
. Unknown
</paragraph>
